We recommended Management to ensure that:

The utilization of all subsequent receipt of Share from R.A. 7171 and R.A. 8240 should be supported by a duly approved budget appropriation ordinance;

The Municipal Budget Officer and Municipal Planning and Development Coordinator review the Annual Procurement Plan and confirm that projects are duly supported by an approved budget before bidding projects to ensure that such procurement is valid and legal in accordance to the provisions of Section 305 (a) of RA No. 7160;

An Obligation Request and Status form is prepared for the certification of the Budget Officer of the existence of appropriation for every transaction to avoid the deficiency of processing transactions without duly approved budget; and

Future receipts of Share from RA 7171 and RA 8240 are accounted as income to ensure fair presentation of the Financial Statements.

